'''泰勒·瑞恩'''（'''{{lang-en|Taylor Rain}}'''，{{bd|1981年|8月16日}}），出生在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|長灘]]，是一名[[美國|美國]][[色情演員|色情女演員]]。

== 生涯 ==
2001年11月，瑞恩正式投身色情電影業。2003年，他與傳說視頻（Legend Video）簽訂兩年的獨家合約，雖然她的演出機會因而減少，但卻獲提供私人司機<ref name="legend">{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/14257.html | title=Legend Signs Taylor Rain to Two-Year Deal | first=Acme | last=Andersson | date=2003-10-03 | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2009-05-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515194222/http://business.avn.com/articles/14257.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，合約尚餘一個月時，傳說視頻（Legend Video）放棄了她，她亦一度考慮退休<ref name="legend2">{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/14387.html | title=Legend Seeking New Contract Girls; Taylor Rain No Longer Under Contract | work=AVN (magazine) Adult Video News | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2009-05-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515204554/http://business.avn.com/articles/14387.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但很快便再度復出<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/14790.html | title=Taylor Rain Back in Action | work=AVN (magazine) | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2010-03-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325215239/http://business.avn.com/articles/14790.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2004年8月，瑞恩與Astrux娛樂（Astrux Entertainment）簽訂非獨家的獎勵合約<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/17400.html | title=Astrux Signs Taylor Rain, Gets Distro Deal | first=Ron | last=Martin | date=2004-08-16 | work=AVN (magazine) | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2010-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100314065937/http://business.avn.com/articles/17400.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2005年，瑞恩首部執導的色情片《上方屁股下方臉》（Ass Up Face Down）上映，她自己亦有參與演出<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/22422.html | title=1st Strike Unveils Rain's Directorial Debut | first=Chip | last=Baker | date=2005-07-28 | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2009-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817134914/http://business.avn.com/articles/22422.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年，她與迪法恩斯電影與托里德娛樂（Defiance Films and Torrid Entertainment）簽訂合約<ref name="defiance">{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/22343.html | title=Taylor Rain Goes Exclusive With Defiance/Torrid | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2009-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511151232/http://business.avn.com/articles/22343.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並陪伴以3,900美金在[[ebay|ebay]]投得與自己共度一天的客人<ref name="ebay">{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/22343.html | title=EBay Auction for Taylor Rain Set Visit Closes | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2009-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511151232/http://business.avn.com/articles/22343.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2005年3月，瑞恩在{{Link-en|霍華德·斯特恩|Howard Stern}}的電台節目中擊敗色情演員{{Link-en|卡米·安德魯斯|Kami Andrews}}、Railee、{{Link-en|芮妮·龐尼露|Renee Pornero}}和{{Link-en|奧羅拉·斯諾|Aurora Snow}}，贏得色情明星選美大賽（Porn Star Beauty Pageant）<ref name="stern">{{en}}{{Cite web | url=http://www.howardstern.com/rundown.hs?month=March&day=4&year=2005&x=35&y=6 | title=The Howard Stern Show for March 4, 2005 | accessdate=2 January 2009 | date=March 4, 2005 | month=March | publisher=HowardStern.com | archive-date=2010-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105044307/http://www.howardstern.com/rundown.hs?month=March&day=4&year=2005&x=35&y=6 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

螢幕以外，瑞恩取得{{Link-en|斯科特·費內|Scott Fayner}}的色情業傳聞博客的控制權<ref name="defiance"/>。

2005年12月，瑞恩宣佈退休<ref name=retirement>{{en}}{{cite web | author=David Woodman | title=AVN :: Rain Retires from Performing | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/24217.html | accessdate=11 March 2008 | date=5 December 2005 | month=December | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | archive-date=2010-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100314065538/http://business.avn.com/articles/24217.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並表達了希望定居下來及開展新家庭生活的願望<ref name=retirement/>。儘管，她已經退休，但是迪法恩斯電影與托里德娛樂仍然與她續約兩年<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/25026.html | title=Buxom Blondes Mix it Up for Rain | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2010-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100314065943/http://business.avn.com/articles/25026.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。退休後，他成立了自己的網站—clubtaylorrain.com<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/25031.html | title=Rain Launches Official Member Site | first=Thomas J. | last=Stanton | date=2006-01-30 | work=[[AVN_(magazine)|Adult Video News]] | publisher=AVN.com | accessdate=2009-04-21 | archive-date=2010-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100314065722/http://business.avn.com/articles/25031.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==私生活==
2006年6月，瑞恩在自己的網站上公佈懷孕的消息<ref name="p1">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/server.php?//list.blog=176 |title=GET READY TO CHAT WITH A HOT HORNY PREGNANT CHICK!!! |accessdate=2 January 2009 |last=Rain |first=Taylor |date=3 June 2006 |month=June |publisher=ClubTaylorRain.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311060401/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/server.php?%2Flist.blog=176 |archivedate=2007-03-11|deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但在一個月後[[流產|流產]]<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/server.php?//list.blog=241 |title=NOT THE RIGHT TIME!!! |accessdate=2 January 2009 |last=Rain |first=Taylor |date=10 July 2006 |month=July |publisher=ClubTaylorRain.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927234755/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/server.php?%2Flist.blog=241 |archivedate=2007-09-27|deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2007年2月，瑞恩由於藏有[[大麻|大麻]]及[[酒後駕駛|酒後駕駛]]而入獄20天<ref name="cannabis">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/index.php?/list.blog=461 |title=DID SOME TIME........ |accessdate=2 November 2008 |last=Rain |first=Taylor |date=20 March 2007 |month=March |publisher=ClubTayloRrain.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809024700/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/index.php?%2Flist.blog=461 |archivedate=2007-08-09|deadurl=yes }}</ref>。她原本可以通過做[[社區服務|社區服務]]和參加酒後駕駛課程來免取牢獄之災，但她寧願入獄。她現在已經停止服用和售賣毒品，並不時出席{{Link-en|戒毒無名會|Narcotics Anonymous}}和[[戒酒無名會|戒酒無名會]]的聚會<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web | url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=7 | title=SOBRIETY | accessdate=2 January 2009 | last=Rain | first=Taylor | date=27 February 2008 | month=February | publisher=ClubTaylorRain.com | archive-date=2017-08-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801193951/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=7 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年3月，瑞恩再次公佈自己成為孕婦，通過超聲波儀顯示，懷著的很有可能是女孩<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web | url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=5 | title=BEING PREGNANT | accessdate=2 January 2009 | last=Rain | first=Taylor | date=2 March 2008 | month=March | publisher=ClubTaylorRain.com | archive-date=2017-08-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801194623/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=5 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web | url=http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=12 | title=IT’S A GIRL!!!! | accessdate=2 January 2009 | last=Rain | first=Taylor | date=25 March 2008 | month=March | publisher=ClubTaylorRain.com | archive-date=2017-08-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801194621/http://www.clubtaylorrain.com/blog/?p=12 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

